---
title: Sesame Ginger Chicken Gyoza Fried Rice 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: Fried rice and gyoza dumplings come together for this irresistible mash-up that hits your table in record time! You'll stir-fry gingery chicken gyoza with shredded red cabbage, carrots, rice, and savory-umami soy sauce for a blend of textures and flavors that can't be beat. Drizzle with Sriracha for a hint of heat, then dig right in—fast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6740d4383b70b98541a65502-a405f731.jpeg
